  "title": "Warehouse assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p><ol><li>Receive, inspect, and process incoming goods and materials</li><li>Accurately pick, pack, and dispatch orders to customers</li><li>Maintain detailed inventory records and conduct cycle counts</li><li>Operate forklifts and other material handling equipment safely</li><li>Assist with the organisation and upkeep of the warehouse</li><li>Support the wider logistics team as required</li></ol><p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p><p>1.Proven experience as a Warehouse Assistant or in a similar role within the <strong>manufacturing </strong>industry.</p><p>2. Strong attention to detail and ability to work accurately and efficiently.</p><p>3.Familiarity with <strong>warehousing, storage and distribution</strong> processes and procedures</p><p>4.Forklift licence and experience operating material handling equipment</p><p>5.Excellent communication and teamwork skills</p><p>6. Ability to follow instructions and work well under pressure</p>",
